                    <h1 class="mb-8 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-black md:text-5xl title-font">We offer affordable yet balanced diets for you</h1>
                    <p class="mb-8 text-base leading-relaxed text-left text-blueGray-600 ">Maximum health benefit without breaking the bank is our core value</p>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full lg:w-1/3 lg:max-w-lg md:w-1/2">
